        "action": "Introduce a \u2018mental health day\u2019 as a valid reason to be absent from school",
        "additional_details": "I want the Government to do this to allow students who may feel overwhelmed and overloaded to relax. The Government should do this due to the coronavirus pandemic having a big effect on young peoples mental health and social well-being.",
        "background": "Allow students to take a \u2018mental health day\u2019 every now and again, without needing a mental health diagnosis.",
